text: * * * WARNING : this piece contains spoilers through the most recent season of Game of Thrones * * * Given the ceaseless flood of reviews, critiques, commentaries and anguished think - pieces that have emerged in its wake, it feels like Taylor Swift ‘ s new single “ Look What You Made Me Do ” has been with us for far longer than a mere five days. Its stunning performance on streaming and video charts and its stunningly - brutal critical reception were perhaps only eclipsed in the pop culture blogosphere this weekend by the season finale of Game of Thrones, an event every bit as anticipated and monoculturally - in tune as a TSwift music video. With the two overlapping in such a profound way, it got this author thinking ; maybe there is more
